race.comment: Competitive affair. WAKU WAKU (7) returned in good order with a close-up second at Eagle Farm and should find this assignment much more to her liking. Strips fitter now second-up and is sure to be right there when the judge calls a halt. PROMINENT LAD (1) has hit the frame in both runs this campaign and will be ready to peak third-up from the break. Expected to play a key role. MISHANI MOET (9) broke the maiden status last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Include with the claim. EVERY HEART (8) hails from an astute yard and any market confidence must be noted. VACILLATION (2) next in line from the low draw.
